{"id":232713146,"title":"《回憶之餌》","content":"跟妳\n借一根髮絲\n垂釣。在失落沙洲上\n願者上鉤\n髮梢的味道\n是青春在\n飄\n.\n赤腳的我\n被灰色悄然帶走\n足跡沈默\n手中殘留的酸澀\n還在\n繞\n.\n海天一色的景\n透明\n記憶退色\n這裡的喧囂很靜\n那沙洲也安詳\n睡著。","excerpt":"跟妳，借一根髮絲，垂釣。在失落沙洲上，願者上鉤，髮梢的味道，是青春在，飄，.，赤腳的我，被灰色悄然帶走，足跡沈默，手中殘留的酸澀，還在，繞，.，海天一色的景，透明，記憶退色，這裡的喧囂很靜，那沙洲也安","anonymousSchool":false,"anonymousDepartment":false,"pinned":false,"forumId":"f8acd3e6-17e9-4d9d-bc7c-bf24d94c2ad1","replyId":null,"createdAt":"2019-12-18T14:32:27.350Z","updatedAt":"2019-12-18T14:32:27.350Z","commentCount":0,"likeCount":1,"tags":["HIDE_THUMBNAIL"],"topics":["隨筆","心情"],"supportedReactions":null,"withNickname":true,"reportReason":"","hiddenByAuthor":false,"meta":{"layout":"classic"},"forumName":"詩文","forumAlias":"literature","school":"捕夢","department":"puff20140930","replyTitle":null,"gender":"M","personaSubscriptable":null,"reactions":[{"id":"286f599c-f86a-4932-82f0-f5a06f1eca03","count":1}],"hidden":false,"customStyle":null,"isSuspiciousAccount":false,"layout":"classic","withImages":false,"withVideos":false,"media":[],"reportReasonText":"","mediaMeta":[],"postAvatar":""}